Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:09.76,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:20.10,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.48,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:06.96,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:14.26,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:20.93,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:28.37,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:35.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I could've sworn it was\Nsomewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:43.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:00.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Around this area, our nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:03.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...shares a border not only with\NShoukoku but also with the highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:09.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the spot where Shoukoku's\Naerial base was found the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was within the highland border.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:15.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,How would you interpret that in the\Nclearest and most pessimistic terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:20.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd have to say the highlands and\NShoukoku have formed an alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:24.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is the center doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:26.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:29.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,For the next few days, the Messis...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:32.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will dry-dock and undergo\Nmaintenance for our return trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:35.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know that times are grim...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:38.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but I hope you sibyllae\Nwill enjoy the time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:42.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's been far\Ntoo much tragedy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:48.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes... And most likely,\Nmore lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:54.19,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Sacrosanct
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, someone was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll leave right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:27.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. I'm going\Nto be a man myself after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still, that really blew me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:39.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knew the Simoun gem\Ngauged people's emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:45.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,It shows you that we understand\Nnothing about the Simouns even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,It does look that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:51.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said so yourself, remember?\NThat first day we met...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.\NI just remembered, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,S-Something\Ntells me this isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:04.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, you said this before.\NThat years ago, you and Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:08.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, Floe and I used to be in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I-In love?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:15.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I didn't think\Nyou made a very good couple...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:22.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I tell you something now, will you\Nkeep it between the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:30.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's true I did harbor what could\Nbe called affection for Sibylla Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:36.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since she was\Na sacred sibylla, I just couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take it to the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:45.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how\Naggressively she pursued?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, Waporif.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I were lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:56.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,If anyone asks, that's how\Nyou'll answer. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:11.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,But a story this funny...\NI wonder if I can hold out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:13.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway... I don't know\Nabout the "sacred" part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:26.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we really be that big of a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:31.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,You feel that way because you have\Nyet to truly understand who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's all there is to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that thing really gonna work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Be patient. Be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've seen it in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here's one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:54.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama, it's amazing!\NCome over here and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:57.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess Kaim's back\Nto calling her "Para-sama."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:14.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a lovely sound...\NThe laughter of young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain, were we\Nreally like that once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:21.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I have a feeling that\Nwe must have been once...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,But wait, were we really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,You called for me, Sibylla Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:40.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,First, let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:50.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I need something done in secret,\Nand I can ask no one but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns must\Nnever be violated...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:55.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as they are the holy\Nvessels of gods, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,And this divine vessel has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:07.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should already know\Nthe answer to that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you can't bring\Nyourself to say it, allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because the Simouns\Nare machines, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun gems,\Nwhich gauge our souls...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,The helical motors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Granted, some mysteries remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, the truth\Nis just as you described.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:33.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns' undeniable superiority\Nover other nations has now been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:37.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the not-so-distant future,\Nthe military dynamic between...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:41.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Simulacrum Kyuukoku and our\Nneighboring countries will be reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dismantle a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:50.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said\Nthey were nothing but machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:55.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,With all due respect,\NSibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:59.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that is something\Nwe've all been long aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,But people have looked\Nupon these "mere machines"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:05.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as something divine and\Nsacrosanct, with love and respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:09.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,And why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:15.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because all we have are the Simouns.\NAll we have are the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:20.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,And to desecrate a Simoun\Nis something I simply cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know it as well as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:39.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we can unlock all\Nof the Simouns' secrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...our country,\NKyuukoku, will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all this searching,\Nhow come we haven't found it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:52.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:58.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,They could've moved the base\Nbecause we found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on. If I'm right,\Nwe've got to check...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:05.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:19.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you're not even\Ngoing to ask my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:23.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just the two of us.\NWe can't bring it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:27.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't think we could ever\Nhave the same opinion, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:08.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd never before seen\Na cockpit mangled so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,...until that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:18.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I could imagine the sheer shock\Nand pressure sustained in that blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:24.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,And then... when I had taken apart\Nthe twisted wreck of the cockpit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I didn't find Sibylla Amuria inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:31.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,But judging how\Nthe cockpit had been mangled...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:34.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's not plausible that\Nshe'd been thrown out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:45.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,In that case,\Nwhere did Sibylla Amuria go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you made up your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:53.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought I had refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:56.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:59.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our neighboring countries are allying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:02.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,That aerial base is one good example.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Without us knowing a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:09.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Us"? Who do you\Nmean by "us," Sibylla Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did Dominüra want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, she said\NRimone's Simoun is malfunctioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a very good liar now, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,If Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:12.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rather, if anything happens,\NI want to take off at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,\NI want you to be my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:21.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,The sum of one person's soul\Nis equal to everyone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:26.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Should you overestimate its value,\Nthe decisions will be flawed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:31.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course, if our comrades\Nfind themselves in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's a given that\NI would take off at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:45.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are activated\Nby its two helical motors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:51.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, to be precise, you could\Nsay they're being manipulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:56.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,And beyond that fact,\Nwe know nothing about the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Waporif, don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:01.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said it once yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,That I should dismantle a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:21.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,After flying a Simoun...\Nsensing that Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:23.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I did learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:27.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,That they are divine vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,That they're sacred...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:47.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just like the sibyllae themselves,\Nthe Simouns are sacrosanct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:57.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I might be about to desecrate\Nthat which is sacred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,They didn't get back tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:17.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just a reconnaissance mission.\NYou don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:23.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think she's still\Nplanning to do an Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:28.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,They say things work out\Nif you're in love. If you love your pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:31.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it makes your\NRi Majons turn out right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on. That's what I told Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:38.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that right, Floe? Have you\Nreally ever experienced true love?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,True love?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:44.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't insult me!\NI'm always in true love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:46.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you be quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:26.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you think\NI'm out of my element here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I promise it's a fine cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:37.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra,\Nyou must forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've looked into your background a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:45.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only remaining survivor\Nof the fabled Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:52.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Today, its very existence has\Nbeen erased from the records...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:57.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,...formed for the sole purpose of\Ncompleting the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,A phantom chor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the rest of\Nthe sibyllae lost their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:12.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,And now you're a sibylla under\Nthe military council's direct command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:17.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,An appointment that even those\Nhigh priestesses had no say in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,You invited me to tea to discuss that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:34.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, to inform you that the plans\Nyou're about to execute...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:38.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...are being watched\Nsilently by certain people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:45.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what one intends,\Nin order to see it through...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:49.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we must all have something\Nto believe in wholeheartedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:55.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something worth believing in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:57.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:14.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether their\Nmystique is valid or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:12.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns\Nare machines, nothing more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:16.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,They are not\Ndivine vessels by any means.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:11.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I found nothing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:20.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,At least, not anything\Nwe'd be able to comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:27.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's there is nothing but a helix.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:31.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only thing we're\Ncapable of understanding is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're able to see\Nsomething, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can see something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:08.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:19.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,That voice just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Let's go see what happened.\N— She's on the flight deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take Sibylla Dominüra to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:31.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:33.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened? Is Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:36.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's all right!\NSibyllae, if you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:38.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae, if you would\Nplease step aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:23.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? I just heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,...somebody crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:47.74,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:52.01,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:59.05,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:23:06.65,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:19.57,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.57,0:23:24.74,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:28.72,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:32.59,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:38.09,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.65,0:23:44.17,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:47.57,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:53.27,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:59.61,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.63,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:07.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shoukoku's upgraded aircraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:12.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...are relentlessly threatening us,\Nand our forces are being scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.34,0:24:15.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:17.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,One, and Then Another.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:19.93,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}One, and Then Another
